Package: em8300-source
Section: admin
Architecture: all
Pre-Depends: debconf (>= 0.5.00)
Recommends: dpkg, dpkg-dev, libc-dev, gcc, make
Description: H+ / DXR3 source for the kernel modules.
 For further information, visit the webpage at http://dxr3.sourceforge.net/
 .
 This package includes the modules to compile. The kernel-source is required
 to compile these modules.
